---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | YourWhiteScreen"
  description="Privacy policy for YourWhiteScreen. We do not collect personal data. Learn how we handle cookies and analytics."
  lang="en"
  canonical="/privacy-policy"
>
  <style>
    h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #111; }
    .updated { color: #888; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 32px; display: block; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 28px 0 8px; color: #222; }
    p { margin-bottom: 14px; color: #444; }
    ul { margin: 0 0 14px 20px; color: #444; }
    ul li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
    a { color: #0066cc; }
  </style>

  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <span class="updated">Last updated: January 2025</span>

  <p>YourWhiteScreen ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect and how we use it.</p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <p>We do not collect personally identifiable information. We do not require registration or login. The only data stored is your color preferences, saved to your browser's localStorage — it never leaves your device.</p>

  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>We may use privacy-friendly analytics to understand aggregate traffic patterns (pages visited, device types, countries). This data is anonymized and not linked to individual users.</p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>We use a single cookie to store your cookie consent preference. We do not use advertising cookies or tracking pixels. For more detail, see our <a href="/politica-cookies">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <p>We may display advertisements served by third-party networks. These networks may use cookies to serve relevant ads based on your browsing history. You can opt out via your browser settings or the IAB opt-out tools.</p>

  <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
  <p>Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect any data from children.</p>

  <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>For privacy-related questions, please use our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
</ContentLayout>
